data.title: Best of Cincinnati
data.meta_description: Inside the Best of Cincinnati® Celebration, you will have the opportunity to indulge in all that the Queen City has to offer – from food and drink samples, to entertainment, Golden Ticket prizes, and more!
data.text: The Best of Cincinnati® is a celebration of greatness in our city. The awards are hard-fought and highly coveted. Each Spring, CityBeat brings together locavores, entrepreneurs, entertainers and other active members of our city to celebrate! Inside the Best of Cincinnati® Celebration, you will have the opportunity to indulge in all that the Queen City has to offer – from food and drink samples, to entertainment, Golden Ticket prizes, and more!
